DESSERT
WINE
Graham's 'Malvedos' Vintage Port 1984
W. & J. Graham & Co. has, since 1820, become one
of the most prestigious names in fine Port wines. The 'Malvedos'
is their premier vineyard estate. Careful decanting results in a
brilliantly clear, sweet, ruby-red dessert wine. Vintage Port is
boldly aromatic and flavorful with rich tones of brambleberries
and plums — matured with time to a velvety soft texture.

LUNCHEON
SERVICE
We are pleased to offer a variety of dining options tailored to
suit your inflight schedule. You may select our Western luncheon service,
our traditional Japanese meal service or our Lighter Fare entree service,
which allows you to create your own entree from the Salad Cart.
If you prefer the Japanese meal, please refer to page 10.
